      <li>Annotate text thereby being able to provide context to the text and share ideas.</li>
      <li>Edit annotations where other users have given permission.</li>
      <li>Have your annotations saved to your profile.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>If you already have an account <strong><%= link_to 'log in here', new_user_session_path %></strong>. If you need to create a new account <strong><%= link_to 'sign up here', new_user_registration_path %></strong>.</p>

